to just show you the roof.

23:52.266 --> 23:54.635
I hope that's not a bad thing.

23:56.270 --> 23:57.872
No, um...

23:58.806 --> 24:00.039
No, I guess I'm just nervous.

24:00.041 --> 24:03.443
Too nervous to
scoot over here a little bit?

24:07.214 --> 24:08.516
No.

24:28.903 --> 24:30.004
Shit.

24:39.714 --> 24:42.717
What a shame.
I thought you'd be ready.

24:44.585 --> 24:45.684
I, uh...

24:45.686 --> 24:47.822
I guess you're just
gonna have to watch first.

25:23.824 --> 25:24.992
What the fuck, man?

25:28.796 --> 25:31.096
What the fuck? Jimmy!

25:31.098 --> 25:32.533
Jimmy! Jimmy, come on, man!

25:34.635 --> 25:35.903
Jimmy, come on, man!

25:37.271 --> 25:39.605
Come on! Got to wake up, dude!

25:39.607 --> 25:41.108
Jimmy is dead as fuck, yo.

25:42.176 --> 25:43.911
What the fuck did you just do?

25:45.746 --> 25:48.113
I drank his blood.

25:48.115 --> 25:50.716
Oh, my God! Oh, my God!

25:50.718 --> 25:52.317
Poor Jimmy.

25:52.319 --> 25:54.655
His only mistake was
keeping shitty company.

25:55.289 --> 25:56.957
You, on the other hand...

25:58.993 --> 26:00.859
That thing that you did.

26:00.861 --> 26:02.828
The thing that you hoped that
no one would find about,

26:02.830 --> 26:04.863
the thing you thought
you got away with,

26:04.865 --> 26:06.567
it's precisely why you're here.

26:07.401 --> 26:08.602
What?

26:10.004 --> 26:11.639
Do you want me
to say her name?

26:13.674 --> 26:15.808
