26:15.810 --> 26:18.712
My super sexy
vampire power, silly.

26:20.347 --> 26:22.214
It's Claire, by the way.

26:22.216 --> 26:24.783
Unless you thought
it was a lucky guess.

26:24.785 --> 26:27.119
What the hell is going on?

26:27.121 --> 26:30.155
You know, I really wouldn't
sweat the details, Todd.

26:30.157 --> 26:32.357
So right now you got exactly
the length of this cigarette

26:32.359 --> 26:36.095
to come to terms with the fact
that for once in your life,

26:36.097 --> 26:38.099
it's just not gonna
work out for you.

26:50.845 --> 26:53.278
Not a lot of stars.

26:53.280 --> 26:56.014
That's the one good thing
about where I come from.

26:56.016 --> 26:58.152
You can see the whole damn
Milky Way at night.

27:00.054 --> 27:01.222
You hungry at all?

27:04.091 --> 27:05.691
My first night in LA,

27:05.693 --> 27:07.228
and it's already
the best night of my life.

27:08.996 --> 27:10.429
I'm not trying to be weird.

27:10.431 --> 27:12.931
God, I hope that didn't sound
too dramatic.

27:12.933 --> 27:14.466
No.

27:14.468 --> 27:17.236
But if we can make it
more special,

27:17.238 --> 27:20.005
if you had one night here,
one night only,

27:20.007 --> 27:21.375
what else would you wanna do?

27:23.210 --> 27:26.912
Probably wanna see
the sunrise at the ocean.

27:26.914 --> 27:29.915
The sun sets in the west.
It doesn't rise.

27:29.917 --> 27:33.387
- Fuck.
- But we can still go.

27:35.456 --> 27:38.993
So, not to sound all emo,

27:39.561 --> 27:41.729
but can I see you again?

27:45.466 --> 27:48.867
I think this is more just
like a one-night thing.

27:48.869 --> 27:50.169
Oh...

27:50.171 --> 27:52.873
- I'm sorry.
- No, no. Um...

27:56.043 --> 27:58.110
It has nothing to do with you.

27:58.112 --> 28:00.179
It's fine.
You don't have to explain yourself.

28:00.181 --> 28:02.049
It's not the first time...

28:04.151 --> 28:05.753
...you know...

28:32.479 --> 28:33.914
That's enough.

28:46.493 --> 28:48.128
I like this one.

28:50.164 --> 28:52.433
She reminds me
of somebody I used to know.

28:56.036 --> 28:58.038
