you haven't figured it out...

29:04.979 --> 29:08.280
Shoveled a lot of shit
in your life, haven't you?

29:08.282 --> 29:11.085
How would you like to hold the
keys to the kingdom for a change?

29:13.387 --> 29:15.521
Do you know
what it is I'm asking?

29:15.523 --> 29:18.524
Duke, are you sure?

29:18.526 --> 29:20.828
Why don't we give you
some time to think about it?

29:21.996 --> 29:23.130
If you survive.

29:28.002 --> 29:29.136
Shit.

31:10.938 --> 31:12.505
Laurel, where the fuck
have you been?

31:12.507 --> 31:14.005
I've been calling you all night.

31:14.007 --> 31:16.308
And you still
haven't called Mom by the...

31:16.310 --> 31:17.510
Jesus fucking Christ,
what happened?

31:17.512 --> 31:19.044
Nothing.

31:19.046 --> 31:20.948
- Did somebody do this to you?
- No.

31:21.716 --> 31:24.650
- Laurel.
- I'm fine.

31:24.652 --> 31:27.087
- It's just, stupid...
- What?

31:28.021 --> 31:31.223
- I fell.
- What?

31:31.225 --> 31:34.493
I was drunk
and I didn't sleep enough

31:34.495 --> 31:36.428
and I fell.

31:36.430 --> 31:38.564
