48:08.355 --> 48:10.088
he wouldn't give you what
you wanted anyway.

48:10.090 --> 48:12.090
Release him! God damn it!

48:12.092 --> 48:13.659
Or else I'll barbeque
all of you.

48:13.661 --> 48:15.661
- Do it.
- Release him now.

48:50.665 --> 48:51.666
Argh!

49:20.394 --> 49:22.628
I'd ask how you were doing,
but...

49:22.630 --> 49:24.597
frankly, you seem
to be doing pretty well.

49:24.599 --> 49:26.331
All things considered.

49:28.068 --> 49:29.169
How is she?

49:29.737 --> 49:30.738
Frog?

49:32.139 --> 49:33.140
She'll live.

49:35.175 --> 49:36.176
You?

49:40.113 --> 49:42.249
Did you come up here
to give me a speech?

49:43.183 --> 49:44.351
Don't flatter yourself.

49:45.753 --> 49:47.054
This is my thinking roof.

49:52.827 --> 49:54.061
What was all that?

49:55.730 --> 49:57.530
Maybe not right now, all right?

49:57.532 --> 49:59.032
