I wanna know everything.

50:00.400 --> 50:01.401
You owe me that.

50:03.203 --> 50:04.204
I guess I do.

50:08.643 --> 50:11.211
Part of the reason we stick
together is because we have to.

50:13.815 --> 50:15.148
Those two young guys...

50:16.316 --> 50:17.417
were vampire hunters.

50:20.120 --> 50:21.255
That old man...

50:23.123 --> 50:24.391
